column1: select count(*),max((to_date('1970-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD') + numtodsinterval(created_t,'SECOND'))) created_t, max((to_date('1970-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD') + numtodsinterval(mod_t,'SECOND'))) mod_t from pin.event_t where (to_date('1970-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD') +numtodsinterval(created_t,'SECOND')) <= '2017-02-28 04:41:06' and (to_date('1970-01-01','YYYY-MM-DD') +numtodsinterval(mod_t,'SECOND'))<='2017-02-28 04:41:06'
